Articles.Content:
I was playing in sandbox mode, the place I usually play, and I thought to myself, I haven't been to Eeloo for 2 years, and I decided to make a lander to go to Eeloo, It took like 5 hours just to get the orbits right and then and only then did I declare that the conditions were good enough to land, so I burned retrograde and I plunged down to Eeloo's White Surface.

I made an eeloo base there.

Danger is my mid' name.
I'm sorry, but I don't have any because the pictures were corrupted sadly, and they are monochrome JPEG pictures, so the quality wouldn't be very good anyway.
